Puppet templates are written in [[ERB]]. 

==== Manifest Definition ==== 
<pre>
file { "yack-bla":
  content => template("bla/yack.erb"),
}
</pre>
Puppet will automatically look in your templates directory.

==== The Template ====
<pre>
<% if @myvar %>
myvar has <%= @myvar %> value
<% end %>
</pre>

